(34, 1, 'Admin Catalog Import Export Fields', '<div class="grouplisting">                            \r\n	<div class="groups group-js">                                \r\n		<div class="group__head group__head-js">\r\n			<h5> Product Catalog Content </h5></div>                                \r\n		<div class="group__body group__body-js">                                    \r\n			<h5>Product Identifier</h5>                                    \r\n			<p>User defined unique identifier for the Product. This works as a unique key for the system to identify a particular Product.</p>                                    \r\n			<h5>Username</h5>                                    \r\n			<p>For admin this field needs to be left blank. In case an option is added by a seller then seller username will be displayed in this field.  </p>                                    \r\n			<h5>Name</h5>                                    \r\n			<p>User defined field for product name.</p>                                    \r\n			<h5>Description</h5>                                    \r\n			<p>User defined field for product description. </p>                                    \r\n			<h5>Youtube video</h5>                                    \r\n			<p>User defined field for product Youtube video URL</p>                                    \r\n			<h5>Category Identifier</h5>                                    \r\n			<p> User defined unique identifier for the category. This field needs to be the same as Category Identifier defined in Categories Content sheet.  </p>                                    \r\n			<h5>Brand Identifier</h5>                                    \r\n			<p>User defined unique identifier for the Brand. This field needs to be the same as Brand Identifier defined in Brand Content sheet.  </p>                                    \r\n			<h5>Product Type Identifier</h5>                                    \r\n			<p>User defined input field to denote the type of the Product. Possible inputs for this field are â€˜Physicalâ€™ &amp; â€˜Digitalâ€™. </p>                                    \r\n			<h5>Model</h5>                                    \r\n			<p>User defined field for product model.</p>                                    \r\n			<h5>Minimum selling price</h5>                                    \r\n			<p>User defined field for minimum selling price for the product.</p>                                    \r\n			<h5>Tax Category Identifier</h5>                                    \r\n			<p>User defined unique identifier for the Tax category. This field needs to be the same as Tax Category Identifier defined in the Admin console under the Sales Tax option page.</p>                                    \r\n			<h5>Length</h5>                                    \r\n			<p>User defined field for product package length.</p>                                    \r\n			<h5>Width</h5>                                    \r\n			<p>User defined field for product package width.</p>                                    \r\n                                    \r\n			<h5>Height</h5>                                    \r\n			<p>User defined field for product package Height.</p>                                    \r\n                                    \r\n			<h5>Dimension Unit Identifier</h5>                                    \r\n			<p>User defined input field to denote the unit of the dimensions of the package. Possible inputs for this field are â€˜Inchâ€™, â€˜Centimeterâ€™ &amp; â€˜Feetâ€™. </p>                                    \r\n                                    \r\n			<h5>Weight </h5>                                    \r\n			<p>User defined field for product package Weight.</p>                                    \r\n			<h5>Weight Unit Identifier</h5>                                    \r\n			<p>User defined input field to denote the unit of the weight of the package. . Possible inputs for this field are â€˜Gramâ€™, â€˜Kilogramâ€™ &amp; â€˜Poundâ€™.</p>                                    \r\n			<h5>Ean/upc Code</h5>                                    \r\n			<p>User defined field for EAN/UPC code of the product.</p>                                    \r\n			<h5>Shipping country Code</h5>                                    \r\n			<p>This field needs to be the same as country code defined in Countries Content sheet.  </p>                                    \r\n			<h5>Added On</h5>                                    \r\n			<p>User defined field for product add date to the system.</p>                                    \r\n			<h5>Free Shipping</h5>                                    \r\n			<p>User defined field to mark a particular Product is available for free shipping. Possible inputs for this field are â€˜Yesâ€™ &amp; â€˜Noâ€™.</p>                                    \r\n			<h5>COD Available</h5>                                    \r\n			<p>User defined field to mark a particular Product is available for Cash on Delivery or not. Possible inputs for this field are â€˜Yesâ€™ &amp; â€˜Noâ€™.</p>                                    \r\n			<h5>Featured</h5>                                    \r\n			<p>User defined field to mark a particular Product as featured or not. Possible inputs for this field are â€˜Yesâ€™ &amp; â€˜Noâ€™. </p>                                    \r\n			<h5>Approved</h5>                                    \r\n			<p>User defined field to mark a particular Product as Approved or not. Possible inputs for this field are â€˜Yesâ€™ &amp; â€˜Noâ€™. Default value should be set as â€™Yesâ€™ to display products in the system.</p>                                    \r\n			<h5>Active</h5>                                    \r\n			<p>User defined field to mark a particular Product as active in the system or not. Possible inputs for this field are â€˜Yesâ€™ &amp; â€˜Noâ€™. Default value should be set as â€™Yesâ€™. </p>                                    \r\n			<h5>Deleted</h5>                                    \r\n			<p>User defined field to mark a particular product as deleted in the system or not. Possible inputs for this field are â€˜Yesâ€™ &amp; â€˜Noâ€™. Default value should be set as â€™Noâ€™ to display products in the system. </p>                                </div>                            </div>                            \r\n	<div class="groups group-js">                                \r\n		<div class="group__head group__head-js">\r\n			<h5> Product Option Content </h5></div>                                \r\n		<div class="group__body group__body-js">                                    \r\n			<ul>                                    \r\n                                        \r\n				<li>                                        \r\n                                            \r\n					<h5>Product Identifier</h5>                                        \r\n                                            \r\n					<p>User defined unique identifier for the Product. This field needs to be the same as Product Identifier defined in the Product Catalog Content sheet. </p>                                    </li>                                    \r\n                                        \r\n				<li>                                        \r\n                                            \r\n					<h5>Option Identifier</h5>                                        \r\n                                            \r\n					<p>User defined unique identifier for the Option. This field needs to be the same as Option Identifier defined in Option Content sheet. </p>                                        </li>                                \r\n                                    \r\n			</ul>                                </div>                            </div>                            \r\n	<div class="groups group-js">                                \r\n		<div class="group__head group__head-js">\r\n			<h5> Product Tag Content</h5></div>                                \r\n		<div class="group__body group__body-js">                                    \r\n			<ul>                                    \r\n                                        \r\n				<li>                                        \r\n                                            \r\n					<h5>Product Identifier</h5>                                        \r\n                                            \r\n					<p>User defined unique identifier for the Product. This field needs to be the same as Product Identifier defined in the Product Catalog Content sheet.</p>                                    </li>                                    \r\n                                        \r\n				<li>                                        \r\n                                            \r\n					<h5>Tag Identifier</h5>                                        \r\n                                            \r\n					<p>User defined unique identifier for the Tag. This field needs to be the same as Tag Identifier defined in Tag Content sheet. </p>                                    </li>                                \r\n                                    \r\n			</ul>                                </div>                            </div>                            \r\n	<div class="groups group-js">                                \r\n		<div class="group__head group__head-js">\r\n			<h5> Product Specification Content </h5></div>                                \r\n		<div class="group__body group__body-js">                                    \r\n			<ul>                                    \r\n                                        \r\n				<li>                                        \r\n                                            \r\n					<h5>Product Identifier</h5>                                        \r\n                                            \r\n					<p>User defined unique identifier for the Product. This field needs to be the same as Product Identifier defined in the Product Catalog Content sheet.    </p>                                    </li>                                    \r\n                                        \r\n				<li>                                        \r\n                                            \r\n					<h5>Lang Code</h5>                                        \r\n                                            \r\n					<p>User defined field to link the product specification for a particular language. Language codes can be looked up by clicking the language option in the top header. </p>                                    </li>                                    \r\n                                        \r\n				<li>                                        \r\n                                            \r\n					<h5>Specification Name</h5>                                        \r\n                                            \r\n					<p>User defined field for product specification name.</p>                                    </li>                                    \r\n                                        \r\n				<li>                                        \r\n                                            \r\n					<h5>Specification Value</h5>                                        \r\n                                            \r\n					<p>User defined field for product specification Value.</p>                                    </li>                                \r\n                                    \r\n			</ul>                                </div>                            </div>                            \r\n	<div class="groups group-js">                                \r\n		<div class="group__head group__head-js">\r\n			<h5> Product Shipping Content </h5></div>                                \r\n		<div class="group__body group__body-js">                                    \r\n			<ul>                                    \r\n                                    \r\n				<li>                                        \r\n                 