(590, 'LBL_checkout_Sign_Up_Help_Points', 1, '1. Eight (8) to thirty (30) characters long.\n2.Meet three of these four rules:\n- Use uppercase letters\n- Use lowercase letters\n- Use at least one number\n- Use special characters (!, @, #, $, %, ^, &, *, ?...)'),
